I'll pay for my half.

92
00:06:16,140 --> 00:06:18,360
I'll leave the rest to you.

93
00:06:23,340 --> 00:06:24,740
Is that beauty your friend?

94
00:06:24,740 --> 00:06:27,000
Quite the personality.

95
00:06:29,980 --> 00:06:32,260
Aren't you the owner here?

96
00:06:32,260 --> 00:06:33,980
Shouldn't you be working not gossiping?

97
00:06:33,980 --> 00:06:39,072
The owner is the owner because she works only when she feels like it.

98
00:06:39,072 --> 00:06:40,980
Nobody can tell her what to do.

99
00:06:43,780 --> 00:06:44,980
Tell me the truth.

100
00:06:44,980 --> 00:06:47,060
Do you owe that beauty money?

101
