109
00:07:12,900 --> 00:07:14,020
Thanks.

110
00:07:14,020 --> 00:07:15,260
Well?

111
00:07:15,260 --> 00:07:19,220
Do you feel even a little attracted to me?

112
00:07:23,380 --> 00:07:24,940
An Ni.

113
00:07:24,940 --> 00:07:26,740
Okay, fine.

114
00:07:26,740 --> 00:07:27,940
I get it.

115
00:07:27,940 --> 00:07:29,540
We're just friends.

116
