CEO Gan, what brings you here?

180
00:12:21,820 --> 00:12:24,100
You love playing, right?

181
00:12:24,100 --> 00:12:25,860
I'll join you.

182
00:12:29,940 --> 00:12:31,360
Let's go.

183
00:12:48,260 --> 00:12:50,840
CEO Gan, I'll stop, all right?

184
00:12:50,840 --> 00:12:52,372
