185
00:12:52,372 --> 00:12:55,620
Let's not talk of it. Don't you see CEO Gan is watching like a hawk?

186
00:12:56,260 --> 00:12:59,000
Drop it. My answer is no!

187
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,580
You have my contact info.

188
00:13:00,580 --> 00:13:03,100
Just let me know if you change your mind.

189
00:13:03,100 --> 00:13:04,620
I'll leave now.

190
00:13:04,620 --> 00:13:06,140
Director Ding.

191
00:13:11,380 --> 00:13:13,540
I didn't agree to it.

192
00:13:19,175 --> 00:13:20,460
   

193
00:13:20,460 --> 00:13:21,700
 We're very sincere about this. 

194
00:13:21,700 --> 00:13:23,980
I hope Director Deng will give it serious consideration.

195
00:13:23,980 --> 00:13:26,460
Don't worry. I'll think it over and get back to you soon.

196
00:13:26,460 --> 00:13:27,980
Looking forward to working with you.

197
00:13:27,980 --> 00:13:29,340
- No problem. 
 - I'll wait for your reply.

198
00:13:29,340 --> 00:13:30,980
Let me see you out.

199
00:13:38,160 --> 00:13:42,240
Honey, you know Director Zhu from Hippo Tech?

200
00:13:46,140 --> 00:13:48,180
Are you selling Matching?

201
00:13:48,900 --> 00:13:53,540
Yes. You know, their offer is really good.

202
00:13:53,540 --> 00:13:57,360
They'll give me shares and keep me on as the general manager.

203
00:13:57,360 --> 00:14:00,480
You should know that once it's sold, you won't have a say anymore.

204
00:14:01,500 --> 00:14:03,300
Yes, right.

205
00:14:03,300 --> 00:14:04,360
I know all that.

206
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:07,080
But the competition in short videos is cutthroat now.

207
00:14:07,080 --> 00:14:08,620
The industry gets tougher.

208
00:14:08,620 --> 00:14:12,880
Now we have a chance to sell and secure the profits. Isn't that good?

209
00:14:12,880 --> 00:14:14,300
So?

210
00:14:14,300 --> 00:14:18,060
Will we just hand over Matching after all our hard work?

211
00:14:18,060 --> 00:14:22,180
Once the money's in our pockets, who cares?

212
00:14:22,180 --> 00:14:23,620
I disagree.

213
00:14:23,620 --> 00:14:25,660
But I already gave them my word.

214
00:14:25,660 --> 00:14:28,140
You can't expect me to go back on it now.

215
00:14:28,140 --> 00:14:30,120
Matching isn't yours alone to decide.

216
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:32,540
I'm a shareholder, too!

217
00:14:34,180 --> 00:14:37,460
Yes, you are.

218
00:14:37,460 --> 00:14:40,600
But why do you think every decision I make is wrong?

219
00:14:40,600 --> 00:14:43,520
Song Ming Mei, do you think you're always right, and I'm always wrong?

220
00:14:43,520 --> 00:14:45,740
Let me remind you. I'm the owner here.

221
00:14:45,740 --> 00:14:47,440
What I say goes!

222
00:14:47,440 --> 00:14:51,860
I'd compromise on anything else, but not this!

223
00:14:57,020 --> 00:14:59,440
We greatly admire your skills

224
00:14:59,440 --> 00:15:01,860
and want to invite you to join Shuchi.

225
00:15:01,860 --> 00:15:04,660
You're asking me to betray my buddy?

226
00:15:07,320 --> 00:15:08,720
Impossible.

227
00:15:09,780 --> 00:15:11,340
It's not that serious.

228
00:15:11,340 --> 00:15:14,540
We're just offering you a better prospect.

229
00:15:14,540 --> 00:15:15,780
This contract...

230
00:15:15,780 --> 00:15:17,660
was already stamped by Shuchi. 
    

231
00:15:17,660 --> 00:15:21,320
If you agree, just sign here,

232
00:15:21,320 --> 00:15:23,440
and we will transfer the money now.

233
00:15:28,420 --> 00:15:32,460
Then we will fully utilize these areas.

234
00:15:32,460 --> 00:15:35,020
We can set this up as an art exhibition.

235
00:15:35,020 --> 00:15:36,100
It'll look great.

236
00:15:36,100 --> 00:15:37,980
And we will make good use of this data.

237
00:15:37,980 --> 00:15:42,220
Got it. Wang Yi!

238
00:15:42,220 --> 00:15:43,780
Wang Yi, I'm calling you.

239
00:15:43,780 --> 00:15:45,660
What are you doing?

240
00:15:45,660 --> 00:15:47,660
You scared me.

241
00:15:47,660 --> 00:15:49,560
