242
00:15:49,560 --> 00:15:50,900
Quiet.

243
00:15:50,900 --> 00:15:52,720
Let me calm down.

244
00:15:54,220 --> 00:15:55,780
Hey, are you okay?

245
00:15:55,780 --> 00:15:57,700
Don't scare me.

246
00:15:59,019 --> 00:16:01,540
I just turned down a huge offer from Shuchi.

247
00:16:01,540 --> 00:16:03,860
My heart aches. I've never seen that much money in my life.

248
00:16:03,860 --> 00:16:06,460
I likely never will again.

249
00:16:06,460 --> 00:16:07,760
Is that all?

250
00:16:07,760 --> 00:16:09,460
Have some dignity.

251
00:16:09,460 --> 00:16:13,140
It's money, a lot... lot of money.

252
00:16:13,140 --> 00:16:15,200
What are you guys doing here?

253
00:16:15,860 --> 00:16:19,700
Wang Yi, send me the follow-up R&amp;D road map.

254
00:16:19,700 --> 00:16:20,980
Don't talk for now.

255
00:16:20,980 --> 00:16:23,220
Seeing your slave-driver face makes it hurt more.

256
00:16:23,220 --> 00:16:25,140
Is it too late for me to go join Shuchi?

257
00:16:25,140 --> 00:16:27,860
- What's wrong with him? 
 - He rejected a huge salary offer from Shuchi.

258
00:16:27,860 --> 00:16:29,700
Now he regrets it.

259
00:16:29,700 --> 00:16:31,660
No way. You must compensate me today.

260
00:16:31,660 --> 00:16:34,240
I gave up a fortune for you today, Bro.

261
00:16:34,240 --> 00:16:35,420
- "A fortune"? 
 - Yes.

262
00:16:35,420 --> 00:16:36,660
Fine.

263
00:16:36,660 --> 00:16:39,460
So how do you want me to compensate you?

264
00:16:39,460 --> 00:16:40,900
Let's go out for a big meal.

265
00:16:40,900 --> 00:16:42,960
Just a meal?

266
00:16:43,860 --> 00:16:45,540
Sure thing.

267
00:16:45,540 --> 00:16:47,220
